<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your Password</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #4a6cf7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .warning {
      color: #e74c3c;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset your password for your JobTowners account. If you didn't make this request, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
      <p>To reset your password, please click the button below:</p>
      <p>
        <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
      </p>
      <p class="warning">This link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
      <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following URL into your browser:</p>
      <p>{{resetUrl}}</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The JobTowners Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} JobTowners. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 